With our steps toward a mutual relationship with the wider world, we will:
Share freely of our wealth and resources;
Recognize our identity as global citizens, intimately tied to and partnered with all of God's children in every land; Demonstrate our concern for neighbor through service and prophetic voice; Claim our inescapable connection with the sacred earth and all of creation; Live justice as the social expression of love, and peace as the present manifestation of the world to come.
